      "port 0: INITIALIZING to LISTENING on INITIALIZE\n"
      "port 1: new foreign master 00a152.fffe.0b334d-1\n"
      "selected best master clock 00a152.fffe.0b334d\n"
      "port 1: LISTENING to UNCALIBRATED on RS_SLAVE\n"
